data.description:
Welcome to your new home! Nestled in the charming community in Palm Bay, this exquisite property offers an exceptional blend of modern convenience and Florida living at its finest. With an array of recent upgrades, this home is a true gem that awaits your personal touch.

Step inside and be greeted by the brand new kitchen, a chef's dream with all-new appliances that glisten under the Florida sun. The open-concept design invites you to explore and entertain, and in the family room, you'll discover the addition of dimmers and recessed lighting, creating a cozy atmosphere for gatherings with loved ones.

Throughout the entire home, fresh paint and floors have been meticulously chosen to enhance the living experience, giving each room a bright and contemporary feel. As you step outside, a newly added concrete patio beckons, providing the perfect spot for enjoying the warm Florida breeze and hosting outdoor events.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'This home offers more than just style; it's built for longevity and peace of mind. In 2020, a new roof and gutters were installed, along with a brand new hot water heater, ensuring years of worry-free living.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'One of the standout features of this property is the luxurious master shower, a recent addition just a few months old. Picture yourself indulging in a spa-like experience in the comfort of your own home, a truly decadent way to unwind.'||chr(10)||''||chr(10)||'With its extensive list of upgrades and prime location, this property won't be on the market for long. Your Florida dream home is just a viewing away. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own. Contact us today to schedule a showing and experience the epitome of modern Florida living!
